  EffectDiscription_ENG: While you have a Tamer with [Tai Kamiya] in its name, you
    may use this card without meeting its color requirements. [Main] Unsuspend 1
    of your Digimon. Then, 1 of your Digimon with [Greymon] in its name isn't affected
    by the effects of your opponent's Digimon until the end of your opponent's turn.
